  <h2>Understanding Falls and Accidents.</h2>
  <p>Falls and accidents are significant health concerns, particularly among the elderly. Understanding the causes and preventive measures can greatly reduce the risk and impact of these incidents.</p>
  <p>In our daily lives, falls can happen anywhere—from our homes to public spaces. The consequences can range from minor bruises to severe injuries such as fractures and head trauma. It is crucial to recognize the factors that contribute to falls and to implement strategies that can help prevent them, thereby enhancing safety and quality of life.</p>
